Turkish Inflation Goal Is Single-Digits, Minister Simsek Says

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 
2011-09-15T09:20:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/turkish-inflation-goal-is-single-digits-minister-simsek-says.html
Turkey aims for single-digit
inflation and to slow inflation to low single-digits in the
longer term, Finance Minister Mehmet Simsek said in a speech at
a conference in Istanbul today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
